About: Ultra Banana is an indica-dominant strain comes from a cross between MK Ultra and Banana Kush and is best suited for evening use. It carries an earthy flavor with a hint of banana fruit and serves as a potent sleeping aid and pain reliever.

Ninja Fruit is a cross between Grapefruit Haze and Grape Ape strains. It features some vibrant purple foilage and gives off a strong, fruitful aroma. It produces a state of relaxation with an uplifting, cerebral boost. It is a great mood enhancer and appropriate for social settings. It can also augment creativity and increase appetite.

Lemon Meringue OG is a sativa-dominant strain is accented with fruity citrus notes and has a sweet taste.  It is a good all around strain and the levels of THC make it a solid choice for any time of day.

The Cali-Dad OG  has mysterious origins, however it appears to have similar genetic makeup to the famous SFV OG strain, including it's ability to pack a powerful, sativa-dominant punch. This well balanced strain can be good for productivity as well as relaxation towards the end of the day.
Sweet Tart is a hybrid that's been bread to contain a high level of THC. This variety is optimal for medicating at night and is usually sought out by patients needing higher doses of THC.

Space Oddity is a cross between Space Queen and Blue Dream and delivers a well-balanced experience that can be felt cerebrally as well as throughout the full body. The strain has a fruity taste with a hint of spice.

Yoda's Brain is a potent, indica-dominant strain. It's rich in THC content, as evidenced by the dense crystal coated buds. It has an earthy flavor with spicy and floral accents. This is a great strain for meditation and is very uplifting. The effect of this strain can be initially felt in the brain, but it ultimately engulfs the entire body into a state of relaxation.
